spec_data.Name: openssl-devel
spec_data.Description:
OpenSSL is a toolkit for supporting cryptography. The openssl-devel
package contains include files needed to develop applications which
support various cryptographic algorithms and protocols.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 04 Aug 2017 11:01:41 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Files for development of applications which will use OpenSSL
